Load Olympic MatchID Keys

Source: R/load_others.R
load_olympic_matchID_key.Rd

Given a sportID, list all possible matchIDs as well as the corresponding event

Usage

load_olympic_matchID_key(sportID)

Source

NBC API

Arguments

sportID

Sport ID

Value

A data.frame

Author

Billy Fryer

Examples

# \donttest{
try(load_olympic_matchID_key(sportID = 113))
